data.title: Roses, Peonies, Clematis and everything rose, peony and clematis related.
data.meta_description: An interactive and easy to use website devoted to roses, peonies, clematis and everything rose, peony and clematis related. You will find information on over 51,000 different roses, peonies and clematis with more than 135,000 photos and tens of thousands of member ratings and reviews.
data.text: Plants The internet's most comprehensive and interactive source for detailed descriptions on roses, peonies and clematis as well as related information on rose, peony and clematis nurseries, gardens, societies, events, breeders, publications, authors, awards and ratings. The website has much to offer for lifelong enthusiasts and beginners alike.
